{"tid":146132,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲肥婆成日話肥都可以靚","createTime":"2017-03-06T22:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T13:57:41.000Z","uid":28031,"like":188,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"083f01a7bf86e27331eb665556a2d6c059c5661b","tid":146132,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:13:59.000Z","msg":"咁點解咁鐘意啲顯<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">瘦</span></span>衫？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係應該著顯胖嘅衫再打哂啲士啤呔出嚟先可以顯到肥嘅美咩？<br />\n<br />\n唔走去著橫間衫？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇肥婆/行為心理學家解答到？"},{"pid":"dba72d18b894ecae46d84827867afe5e46325330","tid":146132,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:15:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e15225a29be7e9cfe0de2799bb09ecef253a4f24","tid":146132,"uid":17645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:16:37.000Z","msg":"醜都可以靚 =&gt; 打扮一下 化個妝"},{"pid":"b122d34fac6fac21fc430fae2ad0369ca3d58985","tid":146132,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正評,屌柒肥人,人人有責</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心想知 把口講話肥都可以靚<br />\n<br />\n但身就用盡一切方法去用錯覺去顯瘦<br />\n<br />\n捉角度 化妝 黑衫 顯瘦款 <br />\n<br />\n佢地唔係好自豪架咩<br />\n<br />\n做咩要收收埋埋"},{"pid":"fedb916f7b1637545d660d12c75baf055c5fe3fb","tid":146132,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醜都可以靚 =&gt; 打扮一下 化個妝</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醜同靚本身係相對  你呢個例子差少少"},{"pid":"8adfb92356a0bc3d5daaa70708aaf6a96db2b84e","tid":146132,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推到有肥婆現身說法"},{"pid":"74be8bb6c939ff596dd6d186bca45406182ec07a","tid":146132,"uid":79355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:31:36.000Z","msg":"肥都可以靚, 要睇個樣丫嘛<br />\n<br />\n但唔好個個當自己係肥苟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc646324a529c98b4577664420420b03ba662427","tid":146132,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥都可以靚, 要睇個樣丫嘛<br />\n<br />\n但唔好個個當自己係肥苟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我意思係肥都可以靚<br />\n<br />\n但點解佢地要掩飾肥去達到靚<br />\n<br />\n而唔係大大方方咁肥"},{"pid":"2d6914cd7925cc65a36ac2bb7eb7791cba592b5d","tid":146132,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:39:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>肥都可以靚, 要睇個樣丫嘛<br />\n<br />\n但唔好個個當自己係肥苟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我意思係肥都可以靚<br />\n<br />\n但點解佢地要掩飾肥去達到靚<br />\n<br />\n而唔係大大方方咁肥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舉個例 啲肥婆通常都肥到大餅臉 N下巴<br />\n<br />\n但永遠都想扮到自己 V臉尖下巴而去令人覺得靚<br />\n<br />\n用啲頭髮左遮右掩 打重陰影咁嚟呃人<br />\n<br />\n如果佢地真係肥得自豪 咁呢個扮瘦行為正正就係自相矛盾"},{"pid":"78340889d7c1e71cb445d8024097bae06ce39268","tid":146132,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:46:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590084ee1e454162a0635198a496b8599463901b","tid":146132,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/065114_61741a2e1ac5248f7ef55eb735772013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F065114_61741a2e1ac5248f7ef55eb735772013.jpg&h=f858125b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"616538136494c95fc6a1ec02145313ff2539e609","tid":146132,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/065114_61741a2e1ac5248f7ef55eb735772013.jpg]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eser