_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F101210_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e8bcec58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3ac4c646e2cef0a8ce240c8e183951985e2c0ab","tid":146132,"uid":44455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥都可以靚<br />\n低能都可以高分<br />\n人渣都可以好人<br />\n狗公都可以專一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女權撚都可以接受男女平等<br />\n教畜都可以教出唔係讀書機器嘅好學生"},{"pid":"49ea8e8e32b12274ec9b59025563357aae909ec5","tid":146132,"uid":65326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:32:04.000Z","msg":"我幾時講過肥都可以靚 唔好一竿打沉成船人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1344c06a187b026cd8a22472e41649bc7e4f6c56","tid":146132,"uid":42453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:34:58.000Z","msg":"無一個肥婆係無辜架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部都罪有應得 要承受社會唾棄<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">皇天擊殺</span></span>"},{"pid":"b01e73c5662e348e4b01b1d6b0267333c7a363a4","tid":146132,"uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"講還講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ab580ecfec64a4368bd0466a79e24fdcb62d89","tid":146132,"uid":89179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:37:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢個係社會價值觀嘅問題 香港呢個普遍社會對於靚嘅定義就係瘦 大部分嘅廣告媒體就可以引證到 我諗呢個應該無疑問 咁所以肥婆要靚就要迎合返個社會對靚嘅定義 就會出現樓主所講嘅問題 姐係去顯瘦"},{"pid":"d61355090a35e13f8ee207a3d3eb784deadcf884","tid":146132,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:40:00.000Z","msg":"就好似中國人話要有中國夢咁，但係就個個都想去歐美移民咁"},{"pid":"6f9d4d8abfacf1d51a3078228766ef85b352a552","tid":146132,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime